data.description: ** MILLION DOLLAR VIEWS, NO MELLO-ROOS or HOA's!  ** for a BARGAIN!!  The rear part of the backyard rises to offer stunning, unobstructed, 180-degree clear panoramic ocean views of the Chula Vista coast and Mexican Coronado Islands, as well as a gorgeous bird’s eye view of your entertainer’s backyard & home.   Situated at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, this charming, 1700 sq’ 3 bd, 2 ba single-family residence in Princess Crest area of Del Rey, Chula Vista has a 4th optional bedroom / office PLUS a bonus room! Excellent for any number of purposes, whether you want a cozy reading nook, an art studio or a playroom for the kids. The versatility of this room is a remarkable feature of this home. Updated kitchen comes with gorgeous quartz countertops & stainless steel appliances. The interior of the house is filled with an abundance of natural and strategically placed recessed lighting throughout. This freshly & professionally painted house (inside and out, including the roof and garage), the low-maintenance xeriscaped front yard, entertainer’s backyard with space for BBQ, play and garden plus the bonus room with the “cherry-on-top” killer ocean views from the upper backyard, make this home a unique gem worth far more than its asking price in this sought-after South Bay neighborhood. Come see it quick!Situated in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this charming single-family home in Chula Vista offers a rare opportunity to enjoy million-dollar views without breaking the bank. Just shy of 1,700 sq’ of living space, this 3 bd, 2 ba residence has a surprise in store – a bonus 4th bedroom (or office?), with walls and a window, is seamlessly included in the total square footage! Though non-permitted, this room was  completed in a workmanship-like manner, like the bonus room, by the owner, who is a licensed paint contractor with skilled drywalling experience   As you step inside, your eyes will be drawn to a beautifully crafted 180 sq ft bonus room, also non-permitted, but expertly designed and constructed like the 4th bedroom (office?), by the owner, a licensed painting contractor skilled in drywall work. This versatile space opens up a world of possibilities, whether you envision it as a cozy reading nook, an art studio, or a playroom for the kids. The flexibility of this room is a standout feature of this home.  The interior is thoughtfully illuminated with both natural light and strategically placed recessed lighting, creating a warm and inviting ambiance.  Outside, the xeriscaped front yard not only enhances curb appeal but also showcases the beauty of drought-tolerant landscaping, requiring minimal upkeep, so you can enjoy its beauty year-round.  On the side of the house, you'll discover a relaxing hot tub – a perfect spot to unwind after a long day. The double car garage not only provides parking but also houses the laundry facilities and offers additional storage space.  For those who love the outdoors, this property is a true gem. The backyard features two generously sized storage sheds, perfect for housing all your tools and equipment. The backyard also offers a flat and usable space, ideal for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, gardening, or family playtime.  What truly sets this property apart, however, is the expansive hillside at the rear. An ascending path leads you to a flat area where you can soak in the awe-inspiring panoramic view of the ocean and the Mexican Coronado Islands, with nightly sunsets that will take your breath away. Imagine sipping your morning coffee or hosting evening get-togethers with this breathtaking backdrop – a rare and magical experience right in your own backyard.  This Chula Vista home is the truly the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty. From the well maintained, professionally freshly painted home— inside and out —  the added 4th bedroom, versatile bonus room, xeriscaped front yard, hot tub, and the stunning hillside view, this property has something for everyone.   Don't miss this unique opportunity to make it your own and create lasting memories in this enchanting residence. Contact me today to schedule a viewing and immerse yourself in the allure of this exceptional property in person!!
